init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The task force is led by Dr. David Sinclair, a brilliant scientist who is also a single father.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Sinclair's team is able to track the source of the anomaly to a small town in the United States.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He was able to deduce that the anomaly was not a result of the men's actions, but rather the actions of their children.
